10
00:02:27,872 --> 00:02:41,830
ALEX: The trial collapsed because Musk's lawyers couldn't prove OpenAI breached its nonprofit charter, which is hilarious because the real question never got asked in discovery. The judge just said no standing, case dismissed, everyone go home.

11
